Both use identical `tsconfig.json` extending `@vercel/ai-tsconfig/ts-library.json`:

```json
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "composite": true,
    "rootDir": "src",
    "outDir": "dist"
  },
  "references": [
    { "path": "../provider" },
